520
00:40:50,065 --> 00:40:51,999
You have led us for many years.

521
00:40:52,067 --> 00:40:54,228
God has led us.

522
00:40:54,302 --> 00:40:56,202
Samuel ..

523
00:40:56,271 --> 00:40:58,569
you are not as young as you were.

524
00:40:59,541 --> 00:41:01,031
We are worried.

525
00:41:02,177 --> 00:41:04,543
Who will speak to the Lord after you?

526
00:41:04,613 --> 00:41:07,081
Who will lead us against the Philistines?

527
00:41:07,148 --> 00:41:09,082
My sons will inherit my place.

528
00:41:11,820 --> 00:41:13,447
Your sons are corrupt.

529
00:41:13,522 --> 00:41:18,016
My sons have been brought up
to trust in God and obey his laws.

530
00:41:18,093 --> 00:41:22,894
Everything I have done for you
I have done because I walk in God's ways.

531
00:41:22,964 --> 00:41:25,228
