532
00:41:25,300 --> 00:41:26,858
Everyone knows it.

533
00:41:28,103 --> 00:41:30,071
They shame your good name.

534
00:41:32,173 --> 00:41:33,606
So...

535
00:41:35,744 --> 00:41:37,974
when you are gone...

536
00:41:38,046 --> 00:41:39,741
and the Philistines return...

537
00:41:39,814 --> 00:41:43,181
